## President's Report

Bdale reported about about a new OSI board, which now also includes the
former DPL and SPI advisor Martin Michlmayr.


## Treasurer's Report

Michael Schultheiss presented a draft report covering the start of the
data entry system until the day of the meeting. It does not include
credit card data. Bdale pointed out that the annual report is blocked
waiting for a financial report.

The 1023 has been requested from the Internal Revenue Service and the
fees for it have been paid already.


## Secretary's Report

No secretary present.


## Items up for discussion

### New Debian Project Leader

The Debian project has elected Steve McIntyre as their new DPL as of
April 17th. He will become board advisor with his position as Debian
Project Leader.


## Adjournment

The meeting was adjourned until Wednesday, May 21st, 2008 at 19:00 UTC
in #spi on irc.oftc.net.


